formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) At the time of project registration, RERA Bank Account number was inadvertently given as 919020037583784 (which is RERA Collection A/c) instead of RERA Retention Account having Account Number 919020037606094. RERA Bank account details certified in this Form is for RERA Retention Account though details of RERA Account details as auto fetched by Guj RERA portal while filing Form-3 is of RERA collection account. This error needs to be corrected with Guj RERA through change request by the promoter. 

2) Outstanding balance of unsecured loans as at 31/10/2022 uploaded herewith includes accrued interest amount thereon and subject to promoter confirmation.

3) The promoter has directly executed sale deed in favour of the allottees after receiving B.U. permission in respect of Unit No. B-202, B-302, B-502, B-503, B-701, B-703. Accordingly, date of agreement mentioned in Form-3 Annexure in respect of said units is date of sale deed.
